Follow DS rules for the game screens.

All Games must follow this rules:

Sequence of the game:
1. A user selects an available game from games carousel.
2. If playable, he lands on the game into screen where we show the instructions and points. If user has played the game, show game result screen.
3. When the user clicks on start button he must see the how to play screen with a start button.
4. Gameplay screen
5. Game result screen
